MERCURIES LIFE said unconsolidated sales
in March fell 27.23% to NT$7,670,976,000 from NT$10,541,517,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  3/2012           3/2011
Sales           7,670,976        10,541,517  
YOY%             -27.23%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           32,399,513       31,033,727  
YOY%              4.40%  
=================================================================
 